query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cc k mk cct1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 k mk cct2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 k mk t) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 k mk t kt) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 k kt mk t ci) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci k kt mk t chn) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 chn ci k kt mk t n) */ select min(n.name) AS cast_member,
min(t.title) AS complete_dynamic_hero_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('fight',
'superhero',
'blood',
'10,000-mile-club',
'violence',
'murder-in-title',
'sequel',
'tv-special',
'based-on-novel',
'number-in-title')
inner join complete_cast AS cc
on mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind like '%complete%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1958
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'movie'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND chn.name IS NOT NULL AND ( chn.name like '%Charo%' OR chn.name like '%Charo%')
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id;
